summary: Just a reminder that Kylo Ren's real world equivalent is an alt-right man-child who fell in love with facism and shot up a...

summary: When will people realize that the sequel trilogy isn't about Rey, it's about Kylo Ren? When will people realize that the sequel...
body: When will people realize that the sequel trilogy isn’t about Rey, it’s about Kylo Ren? When will people realize that the sequel trilogy promotes the exact opposite of progressivism and equality? When will people stop falling in love with fascist, abusive man-children just because the characters has been thrown into a fantasy world?

summary:
Sabine: Why are you standing on the counter?
Zeb: I am a grown man and I can stand on whatever I want, thank you very...
body:
Sabine: Why are you standing on the counter?

Zeb: I am a grown man and I can stand on whatever I want, thank you very much!

Sabine: …Where’s the spider?

Zeb, quietly: It’s under the table.

blog.description: I am a descriptivist linguist for the Mando'a language. I show what it can do, not what it MUST do. This is a place for discussion about Mando'a, and Mandalorian society and culture. Feel free to use the head cannons from this blog (or reblogged from others) in your RP or writing. All words and descriptions are taken from the mandoa.org Mandalorian Dictionary. Want to support this blog? Buy me a Kofi? OR buy some Mando'a themed items? Visit our Discord? Blog icon by Rina
